#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.9"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.9:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.9:0.2"
msgid "1. Samādhivagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 9. Viggāhikakathāsutta → viggāhikā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.9:0.3"
msgid "9. Viggāhikakathāsutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: katheyyātha → kathetha (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn56.9:1.1"
msgid "“Mā, bhikkhave, viggāhikakathaṃ katheyyātha:"
msgstr ""

#. VAR: Adhiciṇṇaṃ te → āciṇṇaṃ te (bj) | āciṇṇante (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.9:1.2"
msgid ""
"‘na tvaṃ imaṃ dhammavinayaṃ ājānāsi, ahaṃ imaṃ dhammavinayaṃ ājānāmi. Kiṃ "
"tvaṃ imaṃ dhammavinayaṃ ājānissasi. Micchāpaṭipanno tvamasi, ahamasmi "
"sammāpaṭipanno. Sahitaṃ me, asahitaṃ te. Purevacanīyaṃ pacchā avaca, "
"pacchāvacanīyaṃ pure avaca. Adhiciṇṇaṃ te viparāvattaṃ. Āropito te vādo, "
"cara vādappamokkhāya. Niggahitosi, nibbeṭhehi vā sace pahosī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn56.9:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn56.9:1.4"
msgid ""
"Nesā, bhikkhave, kathā atthasaṃhitā nādibrahmacariyakā na nibbidāya na "
"virāgāya na nirodhāya na upasamāya na abhiññāya na sambodhāya na nibbānāya "
"saṃvattati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.9:2.1"
msgid ""
"Kathentā ca kho tumhe, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti katheyyātha, ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhasamudayo’ti katheyyātha, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ti katheyyātha, ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti katheyyātha … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn56.9:2.2"
msgid "yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.9:2.3"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
